# Deploy Keys Directory
#
# Store SSH deploy keys here for pull-based deployment.
# Keys are gitignored - only .gitkeep is committed.
#
# Naming convention:
#   deploy_key           - Active deploy key (private)
#   deploy_key.pub       - Public key (for GitHub)
#   deploy_key_YYYYMMDD  - Dated backup during rotation
#
# Generate a new deploy key:
#   ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -f deploy/keys/deploy_key -N "" -C "deploy-$(date +%Y%m%d)"
#
# See ADR-009 for credential rotation procedures.
